channel.title: For everyone with compiler has been disabled by the administrator problem!
channel.description:
Click start, run, and enter this:
[code]REG add HKCU\Software\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\System /v DisableCMD /t REG_DWORD /d 0 /f[/code]
Sorry, I've seen several of them with this problem because some jackass had a source that disabled it, just do this and it will solve your problem.
